1240
01:43:56,730 --> 01:44:00,222
Where is he?
I can't see him.

1241
01:44:00,367 --> 01:44:02,267
Open the door.!

1242
01:44:10,377 --> 01:44:11,867
[ All Screaming ]

1243
01:44:23,423 --> 01:44:26,221
More water!

1244
01:44:34,101 --> 01:44:37,434
[ Charlie ]
Norman, Tom.! Come in here.!

1245
01:44:55,656 --> 01:44:58,819
[ Men Grunting ]

1246
01:45:01,228 --> 01:45:04,629
- I got him!
- It'll hold. Where's the pole?

1247
01:45:11,638 --> 01:45:14,163
[ Gunshot ]

1248
01:45:17,210 --> 01:45:20,043
Go on. Yell out if you see them
come around the front.

1249
01:45:20,147 --> 01:45:22,445
Charlie, come over here.

1250
01:45:26,286 --> 01:45:28,686
Here we go again.!

1251
01:45:28,789 --> 01:45:30,984
Keep goin; Norman.!
Do it again.!

1252
01:45:35,429 --> 01:45:38,125
[ Cawsey ]
Hee-hee.!

1253
01:45:38,265 --> 01:45:41,564
- Tom!
- To your right a bit.

1254
01:45:43,570 --> 01:45:45,765
- Watch this one.
-[ Clattering ]

1255
01:45:47,507 --> 01:45:53,036
dd [ Bagpipes, Drums ]

1256
01:45:56,850 --> 01:45:58,715
He's playing music.

1257
01:45:58,819 --> 01:46:02,255
dd [ Continues ]

1258
01:46:13,700 --> 01:46:17,397
dd [ Both Humming Along ]

1259
01:46:21,108 --> 01:46:23,042
- Give me the gun.
- Out of the way. I'm goin' in.

1260
01:46:27,047 --> 01:46:30,380
[ Scutt ] Keep the gun pointed,
and he won't get near you.

1261
01:46:36,556 --> 01:46:39,047
- [ Screaming ]
- I've got ya, Tom!

1262
01:46:39,159 --> 01:46:41,354
[ Screaming Continues ]

1263
01:46:41,495 --> 01:46:44,259
What's the matter, Tom?

1264
01:46:55,776 --> 01:46:58,301
You're dead!
I'll kill ya!

1265
01:46:58,412 --> 01:47:01,609
Don't come in.
You don't come in here.

1266
01:47:02,482 --> 01:47:05,178
[ Clicks ]

1267
01:47:05,285 --> 01:47:07,617
[ Maniacal Laughter]

1268
01:47:21,435 --> 01:47:23,096
dd[ Continues ]

1269
01:47:23,203 --> 01:47:25,103
Evenin', Mr. Sumner.

1270
01:47:37,517 --> 01:47:39,747
Come on.!

1271
01:47:42,556 --> 01:47:45,320
Come on!

1272
01:48:08,014 --> 01:48:10,539
dd[ Stops ]

1273
01:48:20,093 --> 01:48:22,027
Gun's empty.

1274
01:48:24,297 --> 01:48:27,164
Is it, now?

1275
01:48:28,969 --> 01:48:31,335
Why don't you pull it
and show me?

1276
01:48:31,438 --> 01:48:34,839
I've got plenty of time,
Mr. Sumner.

1277
01:48:38,211 --> 01:48:40,475
David, I need you.!

1278
01:48:40,580 --> 01:48:43,811
[ Screams ]
Charlie.!

1279
01:48:43,917 --> 01:48:45,714
No! Get away!

1280
01:48:49,089 --> 01:48:52,149
No.! Aaah.!

1281
01:48:56,796 --> 01:48:59,230
No.! No.!

1282
01:49:11,311 --> 01:49:15,304
Take him downstairs, Charlie.

1283
01:49:15,415 --> 01:49:17,349
You put him to sleep.

1284
01:49:17,450 --> 01:49:19,975
I'll call you when I'm ready.

1285
01:49:35,302 --> 01:49:37,862
Just do it, Charlie.

1286
01:49:39,873 --> 01:49:41,363
[ Screaming ]

1287
01:50:22,248 --> 01:50:24,307
No, Charlie!

1288
01:50:24,417 --> 01:50:26,317
[ Gasps ]

1289
01:51:51,071 --> 01:51:52,971
Jesus.

1290
01:51:54,974 --> 01:51:56,874
I got 'em all.

1291
01:52:15,762 --> 01:52:18,094
- [ Screaming ]
- [ Shuddering ]

1292
01:52:22,368 --> 01:52:24,928
Amy? Get-- Get the gun.

1293
01:52:25,038 --> 01:52:27,006
Amy--

1294
01:53:04,344 --> 01:53:06,437
Use the gun, Amy.

1295
01:53:06,546 --> 01:53:08,776
[ Shot Fires ]

1296
01:54:26,292 --> 01:54:28,192
Okay. Okay?

1297
01:54:59,359 --> 01:55:01,589
You okay?

1298
01:55:07,300 --> 01:55:09,200
Hmm?

1299
01:55:28,922 --> 01:55:32,187
[ Car Doors Open, Shut ]

1300
01:55:34,093 --> 01:55:36,653
[ Car Engine Starts ]

1301
01:56:00,887 --> 01:56:02,787
I don't know my way home.

1302
01:56:06,459 --> 01:56:08,393
It's okay.

1303
01:56:16,436 --> 01:56:18,961
I don't either.

